 </math>, a probability distribution of 
 <italic>z</italic>′‐sized offspring produced by a mother plant reaching full flowering on date 
 <italic>d</italic>
 <sub>f</sub>. By the law of total probability
 <disp-formula id="ecy3219-disp-0002">
  <label>(2)</label>
  <math id="nlm-math-3">
   <mrow>
